### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 3,
    "name": "John",
    "age": 25
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/users

### Get a user by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/1

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Somu Updated",
    "age": 20
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/1


